j=A.w('Gazettle ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our word puzzle game application.',a6,a6,a6,A.P().$3$color$fontSize$height(o,14,1.6),a6,a6,a6)
i=a5.m_("1. Information We Collect","Gazettle is designed with privacy in mind. We collect and store minimal information, all of which remains on your device:\n\n\u2022 Game Progress: Your puzzle solutions, win/loss records, and streaks\n\u2022 Statistics: Performance data such as guess distribution and completion times\n\u2022 Preferences: Your chosen settings including theme mode, difficulty preferences, and notification settings\n\u2022 Game State: Current puzzle progress to allow you to resume interrupted games\n\nThis data is stored locally on your device using secure local storage and is never transmitted to our servers.",p,o)
h=a5.m_("2. Information We Do Not Collect","We do not collect, store, or transmit:\n\n\u2022 Personal identification information (name, email, phone number)\n\u2022 Location data\n\u2022 Device identifiers or advertising IDs\n\u2022 Contact lists or other personal data\n\u2022 Photos, files, or other media\n\u2022 Browsing history or app usage patterns outside our app\n\nWe do not require account creation or login to use Gazettle.",p,o)
g=a5.m_("3. Third-Party Services","Gazettle connects to the following third-party service:\n\nFree Dictionary API: After a puzzle ends, the App may fetch a single dictionary definition of the puzzle's answer word from the Free Dictionary API (api.dictionaryapi.dev). This service receives only that single word and does not receive any personal information or device identifiers.\n\nThese queries are made over secure HTTPS connections and contain no personally identifiable information.",p,o)
f=a5.m_("4. Notifications","Gazettle offers optional daily reminder notifications to alert you when new puzzles are available. These notifications are:\n\n\u2022 Entirely optional and disabled by default\n\u2022 Processed locally on your device\n\u2022 Not used to collect or transmit any data\n\u2022 Controllable through your device settings and within the app\n\nYou can enable, disable, or customize notification timing at any time in the app settings.",p,o)
e=a5.m_("5. Data Storage and Security","All game data is stored locally on your device using Hive, a secure local database solution. Your data:\n\n\u2022 Never leaves your device\n\u2022 Is not backed up to our servers\n\u2022 Is not accessible to us or any third parties\n\u2022 Will be deleted if you uninstall the app\n\nYou can clear all local data at any time through your device settings by clearing the app data or cache.",p,o)
d=a5.m_("6. Children's Privacy","Gazettle complies with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and similar regulations. Our app:\n\n\u2022 Does not collect personal information from any users, including children under 13\n\u2022 Does not require account creation or personal data entry\n\u2022 Does not include social features, chat, or user-generated content sharing\n\u2022 Does not contain behavioral advertising\n\u2022 Is suitable for users of all ages\n\nParents can feel confident that their children can enjoy Gazettle without privacy concerns.",p,o)
c=a5.m_("7. Future Analytics","In future versions, we may implement anonymous, aggregated analytics to improve the app experience. If implemented, such analytics would:\n\n\u2022 Collect only non-identifiable, aggregated usage patterns\n\u2022 Never include personal information\n\u2022 Be disclosed in an updated Privacy Policy before implementation\n\u2022 Potentially include opt-out mechanisms\n\nWe will notify users of any significant changes to our data practices.",p,o)
b=a5.m_("8. Your Rights","You have complete control over your data:\n\n\u2022 Access: All your data is visible within the app (statistics, settings)\n\u2022 Deletion: Uninstall the app or clear app data to remove all stored information\n\u2022 Portability: Your data remains on your device and under your control\n\u2022 No Account Required: You are never required to provide personal information",p,o)
a=a5.m_("9. Changes to This Policy",'We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the "Last Updated" date below. We encourage you to review this policy periodically. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.',p,o)
a0=a5.m_("10. Contact Us","If you have questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at:\n\nEmail: ckoyuncu97@gmail.com\n\nWe are committed to resolving any concerns about your privacy and our data practices.",p,o)
